<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reading-n">reading <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'riːdɪŋ/    美 /'riːdɪŋ/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>阅读；读物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Reading makes a full man; conference a ready man; and writing an exact man. 
读书使人充实，讨论使人机敏，写作使人严谨。</p><footer>——培根</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I borrowed a bit of <strong>light reading</strong> for my holiday. 
我借了一些假期里看的轻松读物。</p></div></div>